-----------------------------------------------------------------------

How to do a benchmark test ?

1. Run DigiBoosterPro and load from directory test/ file test.dbm
2. Make sure that mixing frequency is set to 44.1 kHz
3. If DBpro slows down, reduce number of channels and check again.
4. If DBpro doesn't slow down, increase number of channels, copy note
   to new tracks and check again.
5. Test  all  audio  modes  available  with  your music card and send
   results with your name to us: digi@kki.net.pl - thanks in advance.


@endnode
